    <body>
        <%- include('./partials/navigation.ejs') %>

        <div class="images">
                <div id="img-1">
                    <img alt="bees" src="/images/bees.jpg"></div>
                <div id="img-2">
                    <img alt="friends" src="/images/friends2.jpg"></div>
        </div>

        

        <!-- add todays date component here-->

        <section class='container'>
            <div class='container__content_1'>
                <article id="hobbies">
                    <h2>Explore New Hobbies!</h2>
                    <p>Like learning new things? Want to share your hobbies with others? Learn & Chill hosts local events in your area - taught by locals.
                        We're thrilled to offer events related to crafting, DIY (home - kids - fun), cooking, brewing, dancing, and so much more!
                    </p>
                </article>
                <article id="friends">
                    <h2>Make New Friends!</h2>
                    <p>Once you've put your blood, sweat, and <em>beers</em> into your masterpiece or hobby, kickback with your new friends and hobby enthusiasts!
                        New to town or a long-time local, Learn & Chill events are always a good time, and a great way to connect.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class='container__content_2'>
                <a href="/public/listings">Discover events near you!</a>
            </div>
            <div class='container__content_3'></div>
        </section>

